{"tid":1639511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"當初你地一個二個話全民日日戴口罩","createTime":"2019-10-08T15:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T15:51:32.000Z","uid":311573,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c53ce02964591cfd1054249cfabd227d079900ad","tid":1639511,"uid":311573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:41:07.000Z","msg":"林奠啟動緊急法推反蒙面法已經第五日，<br />\n<br />\n當初又話全民一齊<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戴口罩</span></span>以示不妥協嘅決心。<br />\n<br />\n依兩日<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戴口罩</span></span>出街，<br />\n<br />\n全日見到<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戴口罩</span></span>嘅人真係得個位數字。<br />\n<br />\n有啲懷疑人生。<br />\n<br />\n究竟全民<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戴口罩</span></span>仲繼唔繼續？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出面平台我統計唔到，<br />\n<br />\n想問連登其實有冇人係有意繼續？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正評：口罩到永遠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負評：口罩不了，諗過其他野啦"},{"pid":"d3066453f9699ab132038ad2dbabf9750469689c","tid":1639511,"uid":311573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ZuBFTt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ZuBFTt.jpg&h=8a1ecbab&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}